snippet.title: Mega Man gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Mega Man, Dos PC game produced by Capcom in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/mega-man/5103/
In this video I am shooting some enemies and I am playing as Mega Man. One of the best games and as well one of the hardest.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
